{"tid":2444050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"越壓越旺》蔡英文：台灣成功進入東京奧運，打開國際市場！","createTime":"2021-03-12T12:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T13:02:38.000Z","uid":337052,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"69195ce4210b15ab44047fa62c7f57c3fb6786d3","tid":2444050,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T12:25:36.000Z","msg":"蔡英文 Tsai Ing-wen <br />\n1 小時  &middot; <br />\n<br />\nいってきます！台灣水果要前進日本、在東京奧運登場了！<br />\n<br />\n這陣子，有日本網友在Twitter上分享，<span class=\"red\">台灣鳳梨在日本超市被搶購一空的畫面。</span>我要請日本朋友耐心等等，進入產季「大出」後，還會有更多台灣鳳梨外銷到日本。<br />\n而且，<span class=\"red\">台灣鳳梨、芒果、火龍果的TGAP（良好農業規範）2020 PLUS，最近已經得到東京奧運組委會認可，符合東奧食材的資格。</span> <br />\n<br />\n奧運對食材選用有嚴格的標準，台灣水果獲得認可，就表示受到國際高水準的肯定。我要謝謝 行政院農業委員會 持續輔導業者、積極向日本提出申請。<span class=\"red\">也期待有更多樣、更大量的台灣水果，可以在國際舞台上發光發熱！<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.ftpe7-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/158625637_10157354878036065_8728454569056524902_o.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=xqgN_oWiXBgAX-L9e2V&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.ftpe7-2.fna&amp;oh=28869a6ec548a97739b7f24ce5fa6ee7&amp;oe=60715186\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.ftpe7-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F158625637_10157354878036065_8728454569056524902_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26ccb%3D1-3%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DxqgN_oWiXBgAX-L9e2V%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.ftpe7-2.fna%26oh%3D28869a6ec548a97739b7f24ce5fa6ee7%26oe%3D60715186&h=86f2f787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tsaiingwen/photos/a.390960786064/10157354878031065/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftsaiingwen%2Fphotos%2Fa.390960786064%2F10157354878031065%2F&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXIwmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=384704b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tsaiingwen/photos/a.390960786064/10157354878031065/</a>"},{"pid":"8bfe3090bd20ae6850842a9295c41cec82fc41e5","tid":2444050,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB